{
  "id": "wechat-channels-video",
  "platform": "wechat-channels",
  "mode": "video",
  "name": "微信视频号 · 视频",
  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "title",
      "name": "标题生成",
      "type": "title",
      "needs": [],
      "promptTemplate": "wechat-channels/video/title.md",
      "humanGate": true,
      "defaultProvider": "cli-claude"
    },
    {
      "id": "content",
      "name": "口播稿与描述生成",
      "type": "content",
      "needs": [
        "title"
      ],
      "promptTemplate": "wechat-channels/video/content.md",
      "defaultProvider": "cli-claude"
    },
    {
      "use": "cover",
      "promptTemplate": "wechat-channels/video/cover.md",
      "aspects": [
        "6:7",
        "9:16",
        "1:1"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "video",
      "name": "分镜与剪映草稿",
      "type": "video",
      "needs": [
        "content"
      ],
      "promptTemplate": "wechat-channels/video/storyboard.md",
      "defaultProvider": "cli-gemini",
      "post": "jianying-draft"
    },
    "review"
  ],
  "notes": [
    "视频号封面显示区约 1080x1260（6:7），关键信息放中间区域",
    "描述带 1-3 个 #话题，@相关账号需谨慎",
    "前 5 秒钩子决定完播，结尾引导点赞+转发（视频号社交推荐权重高）",
    "避免硬广话术，视频号对营销内容审核较严",
    "发布后转发到朋友圈/社群可撬动初始流量"
  ],
  "options": [
    {
      "id": "aspect",
      "default": "6:7",
      "aspects": [
        "6:7",
        "9:16",
        "1:1"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "titleMaxLen",
      "label": "标题字数上限",
      "type": "number",
      "default": "25",
      "min": 8,
      "max": 80
    },
    {
      "id": "contentLen",
      "label": "正文/脚本字数",
      "type": "number",
      "default": "200",
      "min": 80,
      "max": 4000,
      "step": 50
    }
  ]
}
